        <!-- About Section -->
        <section id="about" class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Us</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
				Welcome to The Living Desk, where ideas take root! The Living Desk is a premier coworking space designed to inspire creativity, collaboration, and productivity among professionals from all walks of life. At The Living Desk, we understand the evolving needs of modern businesses, freelancers, startups, and creatives. Our thoughtfully designed workspace features high-speed internet and comfortable workstations that facilitate focus and efficiency. With a variety of meeting and conference rooms, you can seamlessly host presentations, client meetings, or team brainstorming sessions. Join us at The Living Desk, where a supportive community and a fully-equipped environment help your ideas grow and thrive.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Services Section -->
        <section id="services" class="bg-green-50 py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-3">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Our Services</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
                        <img src="assets/images/small_offices.jpeg" alt="Small Offices" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-md mb-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Small Offices</h3>
                        <p>Private office spaces with a capacity of 6 to 20 people, perfect for growing teams.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
                        <img src="assets/images/conference_room.jpeg" alt="Conference Room" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-md mb-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Conference Room</h3>
                        <p>Fully equipped conference room ideal for meetings, presentations, and brainstorming sessions.</p>
                    </div>
					<div class="bg-white p-6 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
                        <img src="assets/images/office-photo.jpeg" alt="Amenities" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-md mb-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Office</h3>
                        <p>High-speed Wi-Fi, water, coffee, and a lush green environment to keep you productive.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
                        <img src="assets/images/flexi-desk.jpeg" alt="Amenities" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-md mb-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Flexi-Desk</h3>
                        <p>High-speed Wi-Fi, water, coffee, and a lush green environment to keep you productive.</p>
                    </div>
					 <div class="bg-white p-6 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
                        <img src="assets/images/virtual-office.jpeg" alt="Amenities" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-md mb-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Virtual Office</h3>
                        <p>A virtual company operates remotely but uses coworking services like a business address, mail handling, and meeting room access. It provides a professional presence without requiring a physical office.</p>
                    </div>
					<div class="bg-white p-6 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
                        <img src="assets/images/private-cabin.jpeg" alt="Amenities" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-md mb-4">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Private Cabin</h3>
                        <p>A private cabin is an enclosed workspace in a coworking space, offering privacy and exclusivity for individuals or teams. It is ideal for businesses needing confidentiality, focused work, and a professional setup.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
		
